cb8b589cf93f87748c00cf25085","tid":2407692,"uid":75,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"272ad70439fcdee45ed93b55f6e19754a81a987c","tid":2407692,"uid":92069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:50:05.000Z","msg":"人地想打我，我一腳就踢開佢。<br />\n之後佢就收左皮，咁算唔算打過交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"肥仔kick.gif"},{"pid":"8a036793e24ac96ccc59abdb8a90b0ed2d6454b9","tid":2407692,"uid":148204,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:58:17.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔 <br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"da00cd3a79decbc8187c7f09b7a486892fac52e0","tid":2407692,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1bff589c79f7b2f9a9f0316fa1eb20284fc5282","tid":2407692,"uid":204929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"打親都輸算唔算?<br />\nP.S 畀人蝦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 所以反擊, 唔係因為我霸凌人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔夠人打，好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾佢捉住個頭撞落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從此之後就變蠢咗"},{"pid":"f347c4f2b25099b961717cf17ac24780ec0988be","tid":2407692,"uid":138834,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"